      <sec>
        <title>Gene Expression of <italic>MCT1</italic> and <italic>HDAC1</italic></title>
        <p>Sodium butyrate treatment significantly up-regulated the gene expression of <italic>MCT1</italic> and down-regulated the expression of <italic>HDAC1</italic> in the colon (<italic>P</italic> &lt; 0.05), while no changes of genes <italic>MCT1</italic> and <italic>HDAC1</italic> were found in the ileum between the two groups (<bold>Figures <xref ref-type="fig" rid="F3">3</xref>, <xref ref-type="fig" rid="F4">4</xref></bold>).</p>
